      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the overwhelming pain of feeling like a permanent failure, and your desire to disappear is a natural reaction to the sheer weight of guilt. While the fear of facing your family is paralyzing, this mindset traps you in the past; healing begins by taking small, manageable steps toward them even when you don't feel ready. Please consider speaking with a mental health professional who can help you build a path forward so you don't lose yourself in the shell of who you claim to be.",
      "source": "target",
